.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
Color: aquamarine, fuchsia, brown, orange, blood-red
Nationality: mexican, german, polish, british, american
Cigar: dannemann, havana, chaman, tiparillo, cain
Beverage: juice, sprite, 7up, hot-chocolate, soy-milk
Pet: rat, goat, frog, turtle, ferret

1. Nationality:mexican == Color:aquamarine
2. Nationality:german == Pet:rat
3. Beverage:juice == Color:fuchsia
4. Nationality:polish == Beverage:sprite
5. Color:fuchsia is to the right of Color:brown
6. Cigar:dannemann == Pet:ferret
7. Cigar:havana == Color:orange
8. Beverage:7up is in the middle
9. Nationality:british is on the far left
10. Cigar:chaman is on the left or right of Pet:goat
11. Cigar:havana is to the left or right of Pet:turtle
12. Cigar:tiparillo == Beverage:hot-chocolate
13. Nationality:american == Cigar:cain
14. Nationality:british is to the left or right of Color:blood-red

.:: Answer ::.
